    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If a plug cleaner is used, ensure that sand is removed.",
        "When cleaning the iridium plug, a plug cleaner shall be used for 20 seconds or less.",
        "Iridium plugs should not be cleaned with a wire brush, etc., as this may damage the particulate film of the iridium tip."
