    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "If the center electrode (A) is spherical, replace it with a new one. Spark Plug Type Cars without turbo charger NGK: DILZKAR7C11S DENSO: DXE22HCR11S Vehicles equipped with a turbo charger NGK: ILZKAR8F8S DENSO: SXE24HCR8S Measure the electrode clearance (B) and replace if it exceeds the standard value. Electrode gap standard value Vehicles without turbo charger: 1.0-1.1mm Cars equipped with turbo charger: 0.7-0.8mm"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Never adjust the iridium plugs.",
        "Iridium plugs shall be measured with a plug gauge (wire type)."
      ]
